metadata.name: unhenged #01
metadata.description:
e9Art - unhenged


i am drawn to the mysterious and the mystical.

it is where my imagination thrives best, on this playground of possibilities and what-ifs, filling in the blanks with wild fantastical speculations.

stonehenge is the epitome of this. it fires my synapses. it sets my brain on fire…

for this is a place where magic and enchantment might still be possible, the very birthplace of fantasy.

i hear it whispering its secret incantations into the wind, my imagination holds its breath and leans in closer, eyes ablaze with anticipation … 


digital art by e9Art using disco diffusion and photoshop, May 2022
